  "text": "In this case, {P \u22121,\u22121 , P \u22121,0 , P 0,\u22121 , P 0,0 } are the generators of global space-time translations. The commutator algebra between supertranslation and superrotation is given by [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] ,",
